    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ren_ng_737378",
        "quote": "The reason we know as human beings that pictures have to be focused before you take the shot is because we know if we're not focusing our eyes on something that happens, then it's too late - you can't go searching in your memory to find it because that light never struck your mind.",
