                "name": "Some",
                "url": "/topics/some"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ren_ng_737370",
        "quote": "For low light, all the light rays participate. We're using all the light coming through a large aperture to make a picture with a large depth of field - totally impossible with a conventional camera.",
